    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REPEATER</strong> is a fast-paced, one-hit-kill arena shooter where falling off the map loops you to the other side. Bend space, shift gravity and outplay up to 6 players online.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinitely Repeating Maps</strong> - Leave the arena to re-enter on the opposite side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/7767ea3bfe1f257c3605c4043ccbdb22.poster.avif?t=1770035812\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/7767ea3bfe1f257c3605c4043ccbdb22.webm?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/7767ea3bfe1f257c3605c4043ccbdb22.mp4?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manipulate Gravity</strong> - Walk on any surface at the press of a button.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/cdd6a84a06a0759507907404b39b9e70.poster.avif?t=1770035812\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/cdd6a84a06a0759507907404b39b9e70.webm?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/cdd6a84a06a0759507907404b39b9e70.mp4?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colour Customization </strong>- Unlock dozens of colour schemes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/15615636135f24126a0c5d5cb6a59241.poster.avif?t=1770035812\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/15615636135f24126a0c5d5cb6a59241.webm?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283860/extras/15615636135f24126a0c5d5cb6a59241.mp4?t=1770035812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Weapons:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Railgun</strong> - Hitscan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Launcher</strong> - Projectile </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bident</strong> - Melee</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 GAMEMODES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathmatch (Railgun Only)</strong> - Earn points by shooting other players (Only the railgun is allowed).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathmatch</strong> - Earn points by shooting other players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cascade </strong>- Earn points by going through rings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cascade (Railgun Only) </strong>- Earn points by going through rings  (Only the railgun is allowed).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt </strong>- Earn points by holding the artefact.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt (Railgun Only) </strong>- Earn points by holding the artefact (Only the railgun is allowed).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
